/*
* Capturing .wav samples and savint them to SD card
* 
* Based on:https://github.com/Seeed-Studio/Seeed_Arduino_Mic and 
* https://wiki.seeedstudio.com/XIAO-BLE-Sense-PDM-Usage/
* 
* During the time that LED Red is ON is possible to record. 
* During file writing proccess, LED Red is OFF
* When Finished writing LED Green is ON
* Press Reset Button for new record
*
* Adapted by Marcelo Rovai @Aug22
*/

